                                                    </p>
                                                    <p>We currently have relationships with Youth clubs in: </p>
                                                    <p class="MsoNormal">Hackney, Camden, Lambeth, Hammersmith &amp;
                                                        Fulham</p>
                                                    <p>And in schools in:</p>
                                                    <p
                                                        style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; color: black">
                                                        Tower hamlets, Hackney, Hounslow, Enfield, Wandsworth,
                                                        Hillingdon, Westminster, Romford, Essex, Merton, Waltham Forest,
                                                        Barnet</p>
                                                    <p>&nbsp;</p>
                                                    <hr>
                                                    <p><span
                                                            style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'">
                                                            <font color="#000000"><span
                                                                    style="font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'; color: #0099ff"></span>
                                                            </font>
                                                        </span></p>
                                                    <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%; color: #000000"
                                                        class="MsoNormal">
                                                        <font color="#000000"><strong><span
                                                                    style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'"></span></strong><strong><em
                                                                    style="font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: italic; line-height: normal; color: #000000">What
                                                                    people have said about us...</em></strong></font>
                                                    </p>
                                                    <p></p>
                                                    <p style="line-height: 150%; color: #000000" class="MsoNormal">
                                                        <strong
                                                            style="font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; color: #0099ff">Student
                                                            1:</strong><br><em
                                                            style="font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; color: #333333">I
                                                            have experienced discrimination and intolerance myself and
                                                            it’s really not nice. Our neighbour called us a lot of
                                                            racist names for not playing with her kid. Then she pushed
                                                            me &amp; beat up my other neighbour.I think this programme
                                                            about tolerance was really good. There are a lot of racist
                                                            people and then it’s really nice that there are a lot of
                                                            people who will stand up to racism. It was good to talk
                                                            about these issues in my class because it is nice to know
                                                            that there are other people experiencing the same thing as
                                                            me…</em></p>
                                                    <p style="line-height: 150%" class="MsoNormal"><span
                                                            style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span><br><strong
                                                            style="font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; color: #0099ff">Student
                                                            2:</strong><br><em
                                                            style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;">What
                                                            I learnt from taking part in this programme was that people
